hicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities insurance funds nonus mutual funds health and welfare funds and severance funds it manages separate client focused equity and balanced portfolios the firm also launches and manages equity and fixed income mutual funds it invests in the public equity markets across the globe the firm also makes investments in adrs and etfs it invests in growth and value stocks of smallcap midcap and largecap companies the firm also invests in stocks of dividend paying companies it employs fundamental and quantitative analysis along with bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolios the firm was founded on august   and is based in boston massachusetts with additional offices in los angeles california chicago illinois denver colorado greenwich connecticut and new york city detailed description bny mellon centerone boston placeboston ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwthebostoncompanycom key executives for the boston company asset management llc mr adam brett joffe cfa ceo manager chairman coo portfolio manager and member of board of managers mr james a lydotes cfa managing director and lead portfolio manager ms elizabeth slover senior managing director director of global research team and portfolio manager ms jennifer cassedy esq jd senior managing director and chief compliance officer mr daniel j mccormack executive vice president global head of distribution and global head of strategic relationships compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloom